nt partner and made a valuable contribution to our broader counter-ISIL eff=
ort.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; But as we often do, we regu=
