<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">But ultimately, I don=E2=
=80=99t think the American people are comfortable with Republicans rolling =
